comment:
* Information needed to make an instant application resolution request.
 * @hide

variables.name: responseObj
variables.comment: Response from the first phase of instant application resolution

variables.name: origIntent
variables.comment: The original intent that triggered instant application resolution

variables.name: callingPackage
variables.comment: The name of the package requesting the instant application

variables.name: callingFeatureId
variables.comment: The feature in the package requesting the instant application

variables.name: isRequesterInstantApp
variables.comment: Whether or not the requesting package was an instant app

variables.name: userId
variables.comment: ID of the user requesting the instant application

variables.name: verificationBundle
variables.comment:
* Optional extra bundle provided by the source application to the installer for additional
     * verification.

variables.name: resolveForStart
variables.comment: Whether resolution occurs because an application is starting

variables.name: hostDigestPrefixSecure
variables.comment:
* The hash prefix of an instant app's domain or null if no host is defined.
     * Secure version that should be carried through for external use.
